<hymn_number>43</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ậty ạ̹lyk yạ fạdy ḥyạty .. yạ mn tzyl kl kẖwfy
 ậty ạ̹lyk yạ njạty .. yạ rạfʿy mn kl ḍʿfy)2
 (ạ̹lyk yạ mạnḥ ạlgẖfrạn .. ạ̉rfʿ nsẖydy
 ạ̹dẖ qlt ldẖty fy ạlạ̹nsạn .. ạ̉ʿṭyt mʿnaⁿy̱ lwjwdy)2
 ạlqrạr- (fyldẖ lk nsẖydy .. wạ̉nạ ạ̉frḥ bk)2
 2- (ậty ạ̹lyk yạ ḥbyby .. ạ̉nsytny kl mạḍy
 bạntṣạr sẖkẖṣk .. fy ḥyạty lạ ʿbwdyẗ)2
 (ạ̹lyk yạ mạnḥ ạlslạm .. ạ̉ṭlb ḥḍwrk
 ạlḥy fy dạkẖly ạlận .. wslṭạn rwḥk)2</lyrics>
<title>ậty ạ̹lyk yạ fạdy ḥyạty</title>
</song>